definition.value: A  quaternary ammonium ion that is the derivative of L-histidine having a 4-amino-4-oxo-3-(trimethylammonio)butyl group at the 2-position of the imidazole ring.
A cyclohexadienecarboxylic acid having the C=C double bonds at the 1- and 3-positions, the carboxy group at the 1-position, an oxo group at the 5-position and an imino group at the 6-position.
